{"tid":565583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"與42歲妻家事爭執  30歲人夫涉恐嚇襲擊被捕","createTime":"2018-02-19T06:29:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T06:51:01.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"81a07bb6817d62c485c2753413b1d8b495a6adad","tid":565583,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T06:29:36.000Z","msg":"油塘油麗邨一單位，凌晨2時許，一對夫婦因家事問題爭執，其間丈夫疑揮拳襲擊妻子面部及以言語恐嚇，妻受驚致電報案。警員接報到場，42歲女事主無表面傷痕，送聯合醫院檢查；經初步調查，30歲丈夫涉嫌刑事恐嚇及普通襲擊被捕，案件由觀塘警區刑事調查隊跟進。"},{"pid":"e78458feb747db8102c2d899579983e15dd01d76","tid":565583,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T06:35:05.000Z","msg":"42歲女事主無表面傷痕...<br />\n<br />\n係唔係條傻撚自爆認左"},{"pid":"133b33e85a6e13cb1700bc064805075e20ed74b1","tid":565583,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T06:36:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03a1895f34210c5e26e3dab74779d32bc1661bf3","tid":565583,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T06:39:00.000Z","msg":"相差12年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e304647df044342ec431c5c3cc3d974947df18b","tid":565583,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T06:51:01.000Z","msg":"條仔真係食大姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}